				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Assignments to learn network programming
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1737975">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							I want to learn how to write programs that can communicate over networks, and while my university has such courses, I don't have time to take such course(s) due to a full schedule.  So, I plan on learning how to do this over the summer, but I can't find any assignments that would help me get good at network programming.  I found some resources with info on this, but I need something to work on so that I grasp the concepts etc.  My searches aren't revealing anything, so does anyone have some ideas or resources that would give me some ideas on some tasks I could do to build my skill level at programming networks?  I would greatly appreciate it.  I also would like tto practice and learn how to write parallel programs, but that is a longer term goal.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
